# 🌐 Web Traffic Analytics

## 📖 Overview
Web Traffic Analytics is a data analysis project that helps monitor and understand website visitor behavior. By analyzing traffic data such as page views, sessions, bounce rates, and traffic sources, the system provides valuable insights that can be used to improve website performance, user engagement, and marketing strategies.

## 🎯 Objectives
- Analyze website traffic patterns.
- Track visitor behavior and engagement.
- Identify top-performing pages.
- Measure website performance metrics.
- Generate actionable insights through data visualization.

## 🚀 Features
- Traffic Data Collection and Analysis
- Data Cleaning and Validation
- Visitor Trend Analysis
- Traffic Source Analysis
- Bounce Rate Monitoring
- Session Duration Analysis
- Data Visualization and Reporting
- Performance Metrics Dashboard

